<item>
            <title>[LU-7917] Remove obsolete distro support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7917</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Its time to remove older distros that are currently in the lustre source tree. Most of those hooks for older distros don&apos;t even build any more. Large clean ups will involved reduces the rhel6 ldiskfs series into one version instead of various older rhe6 versions that we currently have. Also we can final drop SLES11 SP1 support at this point. With this clean up we should look reduces the range of kernels supported for the patchless client.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
