                            <comment id="204928" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 9 Aug 2017 17:48:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;When I opened this ticket I expect RHEL6 server support to be totally deprecated. While its not officially support server side I don&apos;t except people to stop using RHEL6 server any time soon or that RHEL6 server support to be removed. Since this is the case I will close ticket. We can open a new ticket several years form now when RHEL6 will disappear from the planet.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="150360" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 27 Apr 2016 14:41:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oh I see my patch failed due to the inability to test RHEL6.6 and RHEL6. So for this work to move forward the Jenkins build support for those platforms would have to be removed first.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
